<br>
1) pe-su-chi-ra-n-su would be the best transliteration,<br>
but<br>
2) pe-su-to (in katakana)<br>
is already a common word in Japanese, meaning pesitlence, The Plague, really-bad-infectious-disease... you get the idea.<br>
So, unless you're dead-set on translating the sounds, rather than the meaning, I'd go with &quot;pesuto&quot; rather than &quot;pe-su-chi-ran-su&quot;.<br>
<br>
---<br>
I'd have to disagree about the katakana version of &quot;war&quot;, too.  A final-R sound is usually written as &quot;A-&quot;, so &quot;war&quot; would probably be written as &quot;U o A-&quot; (including the line after A, to signify that the A sound is extra-long.  Note also that the O is lower-case, meaning that the Katakana O should be written slightly smaller than usual, and close-beside the U.  This is Katakana's way of showing that the U and the O should be slurred together. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=1129.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=1129.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1129.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.polykarbon.com/bbsimage/addreply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=1129.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.threadControl?topicID=1129.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1129.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm5.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=1129.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=ht